traits.locale_text:
The wearer does not provoke {g|Encyclopedia:AttackOfOpportunityFullGlossary}attacks of opportunity{/g} and can move through enemies.
The wearer's first attack each turn does not spend {g|Encyclopedia:MovementPoints}MP{/g} and does not count toward the attack limit per turn but deals −50% less damage.
<b>Base armour property</b>: +10% {g|Encyclopedia:DodgeGlossary}dodge{/g} and {g|Encyclopedia:Parry}parry{/g}.{g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerArmourGlossary}{/g}

